WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: sw

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Translator: Leah Ligate
Reviewer: Joachim Mangilima

00:00:12.708 --> 00:00:14.842
Kuna swali kubwa katikati ya maisha yetu

00:00:14.866 --> 00:00:16.780
katika demokrasia yetu leo:

00:00:16.804 --> 00:00:20.149
Tunapambanaje na ugaidi bila kuharibu
demokrasia,

00:00:20.173 --> 00:00:22.696
bila kukanyaga haki za binadamu?

00:00:23.414 --> 00:00:28.009
Nimetumia muda mwingi wa kazi yangu
kufanyakazi na waandishi wa habari,

00:00:28.033 --> 00:00:29.191
na waandishi wa blogu,

00:00:29.215 --> 00:00:30.529
na wanaharakati,

00:00:30.553 --> 00:00:33.168
na watafiti wa haki za binadamu
duniani kote.

00:00:33.192 --> 00:00:35.302
na nimefikia hitimisho

00:00:35.326 --> 00:00:39.971
kwamba ikiwa jamii zetu za kidemokrasia
hazita simama kidete

00:00:39.995 --> 00:00:42.978
katika kulinda na kutetea haki 
za binadamu,

00:00:43.002 --> 00:00:44.402
uhuru wa vyombo vya habari

00:00:44.426 --> 00:00:46.842
na mtandao wa intaneti huru na wazi;

00:00:47.752 --> 00:00:53.613
itikadi zenye siasa kali
zinaweza kuendelea kuwepo

00:00:54.357 --> 00:00:56.802
(Makofi)

00:00:56.826 --> 00:00:58.510
OK, nimemaliza. Asanteni sana.

00:00:58.534 --> 00:00:59.693
Hapana, natania.

00:00:59.717 --> 00:01:01.126
(Kicheko)

00:01:01.536 --> 00:01:04.429
Ninataka kuendelea kuchambua
kwenye hili suala kidogo.

00:01:04.785 --> 00:01:10.532
Kwahiyo, nchi mojawapo ambayo
imekuwa mstari wa mbele kwa suala hili

00:01:10.556 --> 00:01:11.786
ni Tunisia,

00:01:12.145 --> 00:01:15.661
ambayo ni nchi pekee iliyotoka
kwenye nchi za mapinduzi ya Uarabuni

00:01:15.685 --> 00:01:18.283
kwa mafanikio ya mapinduzi kidemokrasia.

00:01:18.787 --> 00:01:20.052
Miaka mitano baadaye,

00:01:20.076 --> 00:01:22.912
wanapambana na
mashambulio makubwa ya kigaidi

00:01:22.936 --> 00:01:25.649
na kuenea kwa wanaojiunga na ISIS.

00:01:25.673 --> 00:01:28.457
Na raia wengi wa Tunisia
wanaitaka serikali yao

00:01:28.481 --> 00:01:31.541
kufanya chochote inachoweza wawe salama.

00:01:32.506 --> 00:01:35.534
Mchora katuni wa Tunisia Nadia Khiari

00:01:35.558 --> 00:01:39.833
amejumuisha hali iliyopo
kutumia mhusika anayesema,

00:01:39.857 --> 00:01:42.436
"Sijali chochote kuhusu haki za binadamu.

00:01:42.460 --> 00:01:45.311
Sijali chochote kuhusu mapinduzi.

00:01:45.335 --> 00:01:48.791
Sijali chochote kuhusu
demokrasia na uhuru

00:01:49.407 --> 00:01:50.997
Ninachotaka ni kuwa salama."

00:01:53.492 --> 00:01:55.834
"Umeridhika?" aliuliza aliyemfunga

00:01:56.716 --> 00:01:58.025
"Uko salama sasa."

00:01:58.761 --> 00:02:01.516
Ikiwa watu wa Tunisia wanaweza kugundua

00:02:01.540 --> 00:02:03.603
jinsi ya kushughulikia 
tatizo lao la ugaidi

00:02:03.627 --> 00:02:06.049
bila kuishia sehemu hii,

00:02:06.591 --> 00:02:09.274
watakuwa mfano wa kuigwa
si kwa eneo lao tu

00:02:09.298 --> 00:02:10.666
bali kwetu sote.

00:02:12.222 --> 00:02:16.258
Ukweli ni kwamba jamii za kiraia,
waandishi wa habari na wanaharakati

00:02:16.282 --> 00:02:21.111
wanashambuliwa zaidi na makundi
yenye siasa kali kwa upande mmoja,

00:02:21.135 --> 00:02:22.865
na katika nchi nyingi,

00:02:22.889 --> 00:02:25.324
pia kutoka kwenye serikali zao wenyewe.

00:02:25.348 --> 00:02:28.740
Tunaona waandishi wa blogu
na waandishi wa habari wakifungwa,

00:02:28.764 --> 00:02:30.202
wakishtakiwa na kutishwa

00:02:30.226 --> 00:02:31.744
na serikali zao wenyewe,

00:02:31.768 --> 00:02:35.163
wengi ambao wanashirikiana na nchi
za Magharibi katika vita vya ugaidi

00:02:35.605 --> 00:02:37.242
Nitatoa mifano mitatu.

00:02:37.266 --> 00:02:39.122
Rafiki yangu na mshirika wangu zamani,

00:02:39.146 --> 00:02:40.378
Hisham Almiraat,

00:02:40.402 --> 00:02:43.446
ameshtakiwa kwa kutishia
usalama wa taifa,

00:02:43.470 --> 00:02:46.419
pamoja na wanaharakati wengine sita 
nchini Morocco.

00:02:46.964 --> 00:02:51.437
Mwanablogu wa Saudi Raif Badawi
amefungwa na kuchapwa viboko

00:02:51.461 --> 00:02:57.233
kwa kuutusi Uislamu na kukosoa
utawala wa Saudi kwenye blogu yake.

00:02:57.257 --> 00:03:02.747
Hivi karibuni ,mwakilishi wa Uturuki
kwa Waandishi wa habari Wasio na Mipaka,

00:03:02.771 --> 00:03:04.618
Erol Onderoglu,

00:03:04.642 --> 00:03:09.386
amewekwa kizuizini na kushtakiwa
kwa kueneza propaganda za kigaidi,

00:03:09.410 --> 00:03:13.872
kwakuwa yeye na wanaharakati wengine
wanaunga mkono vyombo vya habari Kurdi.

00:03:14.845 --> 00:03:18.532
Hatua za kupinga ugaidi haraka
zinageuka kandamizi kwa taifa

00:03:18.556 --> 00:03:21.632
bila ulinzi madhubuti
kwa jamii ya walio wachache

00:03:22.117 --> 00:03:24.158
na kwa mdahalo wa amani;

00:03:25.495 --> 00:03:28.495
hii inahitaji kuungwa mkono na
chombo huru cha habari

00:03:29.569 --> 00:03:31.873
Lakini kwa kuwa hiyo haitokei,

00:03:31.897 --> 00:03:35.888
Washington inaungana na Silicon Valley
pamoja na Hollywood

00:03:36.521 --> 00:03:40.897
kuweka mamilioni-- mamia 
ya mamilioni ya dola

00:03:40.921 --> 00:03:43.508
katika kinachoitwa "kupinga - ujumbe"

00:03:43.532 --> 00:03:45.511
neno la kistaarabu kwa propaganda.

00:03:45.974 --> 00:03:51.853
Kupinga kwa propaganda za kigaidi
kuenea kwenye mitandao yote ya intaneti

00:03:52.434 --> 00:03:56.180
barani Ulaya, Vitengo vya rufaa ya 
intaneti vinaanzishwa,

00:03:56.204 --> 00:04:00.181
ili kwamba watu waweze kutoa taarifa
kuhusu habari za siasa kali watakazoona

00:04:00.205 --> 00:04:01.612
na kufanya zidhibitiwe

00:04:02.011 --> 00:04:03.371
Tatizo ni,

00:04:03.395 --> 00:04:08.000
kwamba propaganda zote hizi
ufuatiliaji na udhibiti

00:04:08.024 --> 00:04:12.607
umeshindwa kabisa kuona kwamba

00:04:13.056 --> 00:04:18.130
wale watu ambao wana sauti
zinazoaminika,

00:04:18.154 --> 00:04:22.239
wanaoweza kuwakilisha mawazo
yanayoaminika na njia mbadala

00:04:22.263 --> 00:04:26.364
kwa matatizo ya kweli kiuchumi
kijamii na kisiasa kwenye jumuiya zao

00:04:26.388 --> 00:04:30.671
ambao wanaosababisha watu wageukie
kwenye siasa kali mwanzoni

00:04:30.695 --> 00:04:33.511
wananyamazishwa na
serikali zao wenyewe.

00:04:34.034 --> 00:04:38.596
Hii inaongezea kushuka
kwa uhuru pande zote duniani.

00:04:39.621 --> 00:04:40.797
Nyumba ya Uhuru

00:04:40.821 --> 00:04:42.851
shirika la haki za binadamu,

00:04:42.875 --> 00:04:47.211
limetoa tarrifa kwamba mwaka 2015
ni kilele cha mwaka wa 10 mfululizo

00:04:47.235 --> 00:04:50.291
wa kushuka kwa uhuru duniani.

00:04:50.315 --> 00:04:52.711
Na hii sio tu kwasababu
ya matendo

00:04:52.735 --> 00:04:54.766
ya serikali za kimabavu.

00:04:54.790 --> 00:04:57.287
Ni kwasababu pia serikali za kidemokrasia

00:04:57.311 --> 00:05:01.614
zinazongeza kuwasaka wapinzani,

00:05:01.638 --> 00:05:02.806
watoa taarifa

00:05:02.830 --> 00:05:04.743
na waandishi wa habari za uchunguzi.

00:05:04.767 --> 00:05:07.201
Katibu Mkuu wa Umoja wa Mataifa
Ban Ki- Moon alionya

00:05:07.225 --> 00:05:11.662
kwamba "kuzuia siasa kali na kukuza 
haki za binadamu vinaenda sambamba."

00:05:11.686 --> 00:05:14.490
Sio kusema kwamba serikali
zisituweke salama--

00:05:14.514 --> 00:05:15.665
inabidi wafanye hivyo--

00:05:15.689 --> 00:05:18.284
ila tunahitaji ungalizi wa uwazi kwa umma

00:05:18.308 --> 00:05:20.549
na uwajibikaji kwenye utawala wa sheria.

00:05:20.573 --> 00:05:21.725
Wakati huo huo,

00:05:21.749 --> 00:05:25.622
wenye siasa kali huwa wanaua
jamii ya raia katika baadhi ya nchi.

00:05:26.018 --> 00:05:28.552
Tangu mwaka 2013 nchini Bangladesh,

00:05:28.576 --> 00:05:33.092
zaidi ya mabloga kwa idadi kubwa
na wanaharakati wa jamii

00:05:33.116 --> 00:05:36.049
wamechinjwa kabisa na
wafuasi wa siasa kali

00:05:36.073 --> 00:05:38.417
huku serikali ikichukua hatua kidogo sana.

00:05:38.828 --> 00:05:41.775
Kutoka mji wa Raqqa Syria,

00:05:41.799 --> 00:05:46.375
watu kama Ruqia Hassan na Naji Jerf
wameuwawa

00:05:46.399 --> 00:05:49.414
kwa kutoa kwao taarifa
nje ya himaya zinazodhibitiwa na ISIS.

00:05:50.135 --> 00:05:55.719
Kundi la wanahabari wanaoitwa
Raqqa Inauwawa Kimya Kimya

00:05:55.743 --> 00:05:59.962
linategemea taarifa zilizodhibitiwa
usiri kutuma ripoti zao

00:05:59.986 --> 00:06:03.398
na kujikinga wenyewe mbali na
vizuizi na kupelelezwa.

00:06:03.877 --> 00:06:06.627
Bado mamlaka katika nchi
kama Marekani,

00:06:06.651 --> 00:06:09.194
Uingereza
na nyingine nyingi za demokrasia

00:06:09.218 --> 00:06:11.071
zinatafuta kutumia sheria

00:06:11.095 --> 00:06:15.552
ya aidha kudhoofisha au kuzuia kabisa
udhibiti mkubwa wa usiri kwenye taarifa

00:06:15.576 --> 00:06:17.756
kwasababu watu wabaya wanautumia pia

00:06:18.285 --> 00:06:22.545
Tunatakiwa tupiganie haki ya wananchi
kutumia udhibiti mkubwa wa usiri.

00:06:22.569 --> 00:06:26.199
ama sivyo, upinzani na
uandishi wa habari za uchunguzi

00:06:26.223 --> 00:06:28.622
utapelekea kuwa na ugumu zaidi

00:06:28.646 --> 00:06:30.110
katika sehemu nyingi zaidi.

00:06:30.474 --> 00:06:32.945
na watu wabaya--wahalifu
na magaidi--

00:06:32.969 --> 00:06:35.229
bado wataendelea kutafuta
njia za kuwasiliana

00:06:35.253 --> 00:06:37.892
Pongezi kwa makampuni
ambayo yanasimamia

00:06:37.916 --> 00:06:40.370
haki ya watumiaji wake kutumia usiri

00:06:41.415 --> 00:06:43.681
Lakini inapokuja kwenye udhibiti,

00:06:43.705 --> 00:06:46.016
haileti picha nzuri.

00:06:46.430 --> 00:06:48.248
Ndio, kunatatizo kubwa

00:06:48.272 --> 00:06:51.535
la taarifa za siasa kali kuenea
kote kwenye mitandao ya intaneti

00:06:51.559 --> 00:06:55.092
Na Facebook, YouTube na Twitter
ni kati ya makampuni mengi

00:06:55.116 --> 00:06:59.543
ambayo wameripoti kushusha mamia
ya maelfu ya vipande vya taarifa

00:06:59.567 --> 00:07:01.147
na kuzima akaunti

00:07:01.171 --> 00:07:03.651
ambazo zinahusianishwa
na maneno ya siasa kali

00:07:03.675 --> 00:07:07.995
Tatizo ni utaratibu wao wa
kutekeleza sheria haueleweki kabisa

00:07:08.019 --> 00:07:10.007
na kuna uharibifu mkubwa.

00:07:10.031 --> 00:07:12.749
Kwa mfano, lyad el- Baghdadi,

00:07:13.336 --> 00:07:15.972
mwanaharakati anayekejeli
ISIS kupitia Twitter.

00:07:15.996 --> 00:07:17.812
akaunti yake ilizimwa,

00:07:17.836 --> 00:07:21.361
kwasababu jina la ubini wake
linafanana na kiongozi mkubwa wa ISIS.

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:23.191
Disemba iliyopita,

00:07:23.215 --> 00:07:24.834
wanawake wenye majina ya Isis, 

00:07:24.858 --> 00:07:28.310
ambalo pia ni jina la Mungu wa kike
Misri

00:07:28.334 --> 00:07:30.217
akaunti zao zilizimwa

00:07:30.562 --> 00:07:32.178
Na huyu mwanamke,

00:07:32.202 --> 00:07:35.307
anayeishi nchini Marekani
na ni Programa wa Kompyuta

00:07:35.331 --> 00:07:39.057
aliripoti juu mtandao wa Twitter
kuhusu kuzimiwa kwenye Facebook

00:07:39.081 --> 00:07:42.774
aliweza kuonwa na vyombo vya habari
na kufanya wamrudishie akaunti yake.

00:07:42.798 --> 00:07:45.486
Ila hicho ndio alichofanya--
kuonwa na vyombo vya habari

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:47.349
Na waandishi wa habari hawaponi

00:07:47.373 --> 00:07:48.547
David Thomson,

00:07:48.571 --> 00:07:51.969
mtaalamu wa ugaidi na mtangazaji
wa Radio ya Kimataifa ya Ufaransa,

00:07:51.993 --> 00:07:55.556
ripoti zake zilifutwa kwenye
akaunti yake Facebook

00:07:55.580 --> 00:07:58.369
na akaunti yake ikazimwa
kwa siku chache,

00:07:58.393 --> 00:08:02.294
kwasababu zilikuwa na picha
zenye bendera za ISIS,

00:08:02.318 --> 00:08:04.374
ingawa alikuwa anaripoti kuhusu ISIS

00:08:04.398 --> 00:08:05.576
sio kuhamasisha.

00:08:06.073 --> 00:08:09.062
Na pia tuna hadithi kutoka kwa watu
kama mtu wa Misri,

00:08:09.086 --> 00:08:10.703
Ahmed Abdellahy,

00:08:10.727 --> 00:08:15.870
aliyeripoti hivi karibuni tukio
la Washington DC

00:08:15.894 --> 00:08:18.068
kuwa majadiliano yake 
na wenye siasa kali--

00:08:18.092 --> 00:08:24.405
hutumia muda wake kwenye mitandao ya jamii
kujadiliana na wafuasi wa ISIS

00:08:24.429 --> 00:08:26.436
kujaribu kuwabadili mawazo--

00:08:26.961 --> 00:08:31.956
baadhi ya majadiliano yake
na wenye siasa kali hufutwa,

00:08:31.980 --> 00:08:35.027
ambapo anaamini kuna athari
katika kuyakinga

00:08:35.051 --> 00:08:36.938
kutoka kwenye mtazamo mwingine.

00:08:38.037 --> 00:08:42.422
Haiko wazi ikiwa mtandao wa Facebook
kama unaelewa kiasi

00:08:42.446 --> 00:08:43.958
cha uharibifu mkubwa,

00:08:43.982 --> 00:08:45.814
au makampuni mengine pia.

00:08:46.378 --> 00:08:49.992
Lakini tunajua kwamba uandishi wa habari
uanaharakati na mijadala ya umma

00:08:50.016 --> 00:08:54.136
inanyamazishwa katika juhudi za
kuweka muhuri maneno ya siasa kali.

00:08:55.218 --> 00:08:59.459
Hivyo kwa makampuni haya kuwa na nguvu
sana kuhusu mihadhara ya umma,

00:08:59.483 --> 00:09:01.077
yanahitaji kuwajibishwa.

00:09:01.101 --> 00:09:03.982
Yanahitaji kufanya tathmini yakinifu

00:09:04.006 --> 00:09:08.523
na kuainisha na kutatua matatizo
ambayo tunayaona wazi.

00:09:08.547 --> 00:09:12.323
Yanahitaji kuwa wazi zaidi
kuhusu njia zao za utekelezaji sheria,

00:09:12.347 --> 00:09:15.749
na wanahitaji kuwa wazi kwa mbinu
za ukataji rufaa na kutoa malalamiko,

00:09:15.773 --> 00:09:18.117
ili watu waweze kurudishiwa
vitu walivyoandika.

00:09:18.460 --> 00:09:21.653
Sasa, nimekuwa nikiongea kwa
dakika kumi zilizopita

00:09:21.677 --> 00:09:25.792
kuhusu jinsi serikali na makampuni
wanavyoleta ugumu zaidi

00:09:25.816 --> 00:09:27.152
kwa watu kama hawa.

00:09:27.176 --> 00:09:30.659
Hii ni picha ya wanachama wa
mtandao wa vyombo vya habari vya raia,

00:09:30.683 --> 00:09:31.834
Sauti za Dunia,

00:09:31.858 --> 00:09:33.951
niliyosaidia kuanzisha miaka 10 
iliyopita

00:09:33.975 --> 00:09:35.971
na rafiki yangu Ethan Zuckerman.

00:09:35.995 --> 00:09:40.465
Inafurahisha, karibia miaka 5 iliyopita
mara baada ya Mapinduzi ya Uarabuni,

00:09:40.489 --> 00:09:43.146
mwanasayansi wa data Gilad Lotan

00:09:43.170 --> 00:09:48.087
aliunda ramani ya mtandao
wa watu katika Sauti za Dunia

00:09:48.111 --> 00:09:51.033
waliokuwa wakitumia Twitter wakati
wa Mapinduzi ya Uarabuni.

00:09:51.057 --> 00:09:56.275
Na aligundua kwamba wengi wa hawa watu
walitumika kama kiungo cha mawasiliano

00:09:56.299 --> 00:09:58.163
kati ya wanaharakati na waandishi

00:09:58.187 --> 00:10:01.212
kipindi chote cha mapinduzi
ya Tunisia na Misri.

00:10:01.236 --> 00:10:05.947
Tunatakiwa tuhakikishe kwamba
watu hawa hawaendelei kuishi tu,

00:10:06.526 --> 00:10:09.012
bali wanaweza kuendelea kufanikiwa.

00:10:09.036 --> 00:10:10.690
Wengi wao bado wanafanya kazi,

00:10:10.714 --> 00:10:12.790
zaidi ya wale waliokwenda jela

00:10:12.814 --> 00:10:15.733
au wako mafichoni au vizuizini.

00:10:16.488 --> 00:10:17.844
Duniani kote,

00:10:18.330 --> 00:10:21.647
watu ambao wamechoshwa na
hofu na kuonewa

00:10:21.671 --> 00:10:25.121
wanaunganika katika jumuia zao
na kuvuka mipaka.

00:10:25.145 --> 00:10:29.408
Tunatakiwa tufanye kila tunachoweza
kusukuma serikali zetu na makampuni

00:10:29.432 --> 00:10:32.368
kufanya kazi bora zaidi
katika kulinda haki zao.

00:10:32.392 --> 00:10:34.377
Tunatakiwa pia tuwe wafikirivu zaidi

00:10:34.401 --> 00:10:39.246
kuhusu jinsi sisi wenyewe, kisiasa, wateja
na chaguzi za biashara

00:10:39.270 --> 00:10:41.939
zinavyoathiri watu kama hawa duniani kote.

00:10:42.932 --> 00:10:45.364
Pia, ikiwa unafuatilia taarifa za habari

00:10:45.388 --> 00:10:48.656
inaonyesha wazi kwamba
hiyo pekee haitoshi.

00:10:49.514 --> 00:10:53.274
Tunatakiwa tuchukue wajibu binafsi
kwa kujiunga--

00:10:53.298 --> 00:10:56.156
au hata kidogo kuunga mkono--

00:10:56.739 --> 00:11:00.260
mazingira ya ukuaji 
wa makundi binafsi

00:11:00.284 --> 00:11:02.370
ambayo yanapigania hakijamii,

00:11:02.394 --> 00:11:04.457
mazingira endelevu,

00:11:04.481 --> 00:11:06.044
uwajibikaji wa serikali

00:11:06.068 --> 00:11:07.945
haki za binadamu, uhuru wa habari

00:11:07.969 --> 00:11:09.525
na intaneti huru na wazi,

00:11:09.549 --> 00:11:11.305
duniani kote

00:11:11.329 --> 00:11:16.040
Nina amini kwamba, hatimaye
tunaweza kuishinda

00:11:16.064 --> 00:11:22.522
mitandao ya kidigitali iliyowezeshwa
ya siasa kali, siasa za fujo na chuki.

00:11:23.199 --> 00:11:24.379
Lakini...

00:11:24.924 --> 00:11:31.648
tunatakiwa tufanye hivi kwa kuongeza
mitandao ya dunia

00:11:31.672 --> 00:11:33.460
ya raia duniani kote,

00:11:33.484 --> 00:11:37.264
ikiwezeshwa na watu ambao
